title: Yeah Dawg - Pop-up Food Cart
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Fast food, Take-out only
description: The first vegan hot dog cart in NYC, serving street style food since spring 2013. Offers soy free and gluten free dawgs made from vegetables, seeds, herbs, spices, and gluten-free flour, then covered with a variety of toppings. Pop-up food cart is still operating as of Feb 2016. Check facebook page for location details.
